title: Dishwasher Countertop Bracket
description: Dishwasher Countertop Bracket ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 5 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11700868 Manufacturer Part Number WD01X21740 This mounting bracket is manufactured to secure your dishwasher to your countertop.
